                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No official record of the substance of this informal conversation was kept. The
                    information set forth above is derived from the Log, <hi rend="italic"
                    >ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_523">p. 523</ref>, and Elliott Roosevelt, p. 81.
                    Neither of these sources indicates <pb facs="0665" n="579" xml:id="pg_579"/> the
                    substance of the discussion, but the presence of Leathers, the British Minister
                    of War Transport, makes it likely that shipping problems were considered.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
